              Join our community of NGOs and volunteers to create positive
              change. Together, we can transform lives and build a better future.
            </motion.p>
            <motion.div
              className="flex flex-wrap gap-3"
              initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 30 }}
              animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
              transition={{
                duration: 0.8,
                delay: 0.4,
                type: 'spring',
                stiffness: 100,
              }}
            >
